	R1. The system must notify the changes in the education center.	
	R1.1. The education center's responsible must notify the changes when the message "change in the education center" is received.	
		To do so, one of the following alternatives must be chosen:
	R1.1.1. The education center's responsible must perform generic task (Check the contract - Modify the contract with the new changes - Notify the changes appending the contract).	
	R1.1.1.1. The education center's responsible must check the contract if the contract is modified, making use of education center's database.	
	R1.1.1.2. The education center's responsible must modify the contract with the new changes.	
	R1.1.1.3. The education center's responsible must notify the changes appending the contract, making use of the changed contract signed by TicTae.	
	R1.1.2. The education center's responsible must notify the changes directly if the contract is not modified.	
	R1.2. The administrator must update the contract, making use of ticTae database.	
	R1.3. The education center's responsible must update the contract if the contract is received, making use of education center's database.	
	R1.4. The administrator must send the agreement on the changes to the education center, making use of the contract signed by TicTae.	
	R1.5. The administrator must cancel the gateway until further notice if the changes are not accepted.	
	R1.6. The administrator must analyze the changes.	
	

